titles.title: 杖と剣のウィストリア

data.title: Tsue to Tsurugi no Wistoria
data.title_japanese: 杖と剣のウィストリア
data.synopsis:
Will Serfort dreams of keeping his promise to a childhood friend by becoming a Magia Vander, one of the mighty magicians who sit atop the Wizard's Tower. However, he is unable to cast even the simplest of spells, leaving him to fight dungeon monsters to earn credits at Regarden Magical Academy. As if that weren't enough, he finds himself putting his sword skills to the test against a bullying professor!

(Source: Kodansha USA)

data.title: Sorairo Utility (TV)
data.synopsis:
High schooler Minami Aoba has no strengths or aspirations and worries that she will graduate as a mere "villager A." In search of her uniqueness, she comes across a golf driving range and is approached by the part-timer and genius golfer Haruka Akane. That is Minami's first encounter with golf. Together with the Haruka and influencer Ayaka Hoshimi, the unremarkable Minami aims for the moment when she becomes a protagonist.

(Source: MAL News)
